Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:15.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣き出しそうな顔で憂う低い空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:20.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苛立ち混じりの唾を吐く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:28.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが壊れそうな不安抱いて明日に怯え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:33.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明後日ばっか見てたって答えは出ないことだって分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:38.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限りなく広がる真っ白な
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:42.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:51.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現実が染ゆく真っ暗な
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:56.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:00.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もがき輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:15.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰沉低空下你一臉彷彿要哭出來的憂鬱表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:20.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混雜焦慮的抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:28.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕破碎而恐懼明天來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:33.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡明白就算一味期待後天也無法找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:38.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若前途無限光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:42.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們還能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:51.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若現實早已被黑暗所染
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:56.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們又能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:00.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有以抗爭展現光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近街上多了很多黃色的人誒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說黃巾賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有謠言說砍人魔是DOLLARS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我們沒有你的話就……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近他怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時不時會來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久還剛來過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得東京的空氣很渾濁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛔蟲 蛔蟲 蛔蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限りなく広がる真っ白な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若前途無限光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:31.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:31.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們還能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:40.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現実が染ゆく真っ暗な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:40.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若現實早已被黑暗所染
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:44.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:44.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們又能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:49.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もがき輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:49.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有以抗爭展現光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說剛剛有來良學園的學生被砍人魔襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是亂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如假包換
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是襲擊了一年級的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打個電話 先潛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}ROM是Read Only Member的省略型 意思是『只看別人留言自己不發言的人』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似不是你的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是有些擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道事件發生在哪一帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在首都高速沿線地鐵的東池袋站不遠處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那附近聚集著很多巡邏車我想很容易認出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思 我要下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽頓你要去湊熱鬧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}賽頓退出聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話打通了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是現在在警察那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是現場目擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}田中太郎退出聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}甘樂退出聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}現在聊天室裡無人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}罪歌進入聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}我砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}想要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}人類 強大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}問誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}誰? 強大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}期望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起這系列血腥事件的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟與一個少女的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我的過去有著緊密的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的我對此還渾然未知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}想要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}物情騷然:是指世間很多騷亂 很不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
